![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a1fb50ac-b8e6-46c2-855a-23170ab47854/20240603_170751.jpg)

Alba Fyre and Isla Dawn have their eyes on Bianca Belair and Jade Cargill's Women’s Tag Team Championships as Raw opens

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/26a52c23-060d-4b85-8eda-17a55a9d6828/Screenshot_20240603_170622.jpg)

Liv is out to thank everyone for being part of the Liv Morgan revenge tour. She pats herself on the back for retiring Becky Lynch and says the cherry on top was making out with Dominik Mysterio.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a36833cb-b1db-4152-956b-4b3360478b9b/Screenshot_20240603_170901.jpg)

Dom says he wants nothing to do with Liv and when Mami comes back, she’s going to end Liv.

Liv says Rhea is going to end Dom as well. But Liv is going to make it worth it.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4f8be0f3-22c9-4394-ace3-09e2244a4076/Screenshot_20240603_171024.jpg)

Liv starts to feel down Dom's body and Finn Balor interrupted before she could change the rating of the TV show.

Liv says she’ll leave.. But what if Dom doesn’t want her to…..

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4210ca16-ddaf-4a89-8c2d-9a133fbc5067/Screenshot_20240603_171032.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1f3b4c0a-876d-450b-8fca-995698eba148/Screenshot_20240603_171328.jpg)

Sheamus says maybe Gunther has been holding Ludwig Keiser back. He wants to find out tonight.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8d084053-cbd6-4eaf-ae06-98a53853e845/Screenshot_20240603_171449.jpg)

Ludwig Keiser attacks Sheamus during his entrance so we don’t get TOO MANY LIMES tonight. Sad face.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0b55ca50-80aa-4a37-a9fb-369550a1afe6/Screenshot_20240603_172041.jpg)

*   ## **_LUDWIG KEISER DEF. SHEAMUS_**
    

Very stiff match here. Fun stuff. Keiser worked Sheamus knee the entire match and eventually paid it off by kicking Sheamus legs out from under him as he was on the turnbuckle. Easy pinfall after that.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8ecde61c-4134-4ed5-bf48-6f0e6621f633/Screenshot_20240603_173315.jpg)

Dom tells Judgement Day that he can’t help it if women love him. Damien Priest walks in. Finn Balor tries to tell him it’s taken care of. He doesn’t believe it. Tells Dom not to get burned playing with fire.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4db67464-a565-420b-9eca-c80bde72aabd/Screenshot_20240603_173325.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/233c367b-b5d7-412a-becd-457ef5479c9b/Screenshot_20240603_174140.jpg)

A video package plays for Dragon Lee before the next match

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/85401404-a00e-4a9b-bf5a-e686a21683fd/Screenshot_20240603_174425.jpg)

*   ## **_FINN BALOR DEF. DRAGON LEE_**
    

Pretty good match with glimpses of greatness. Match ends when Carlito and JD's interference allows Balor to take advantage.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/853b6586-7084-4e90-a063-ec08e3bc7298/Screenshot_20240603_175226.jpg)

Braun Strowman and Rey Mysterio come out to run Judgement Day off as they jumped Dragon Lee after the match.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3901f11d-5be1-4771-9289-f410db5b684f/Screenshot_20240603_175935.jpg)

Damien Priest wants Carlito to help solve their Braun Strowman problem. They walk off and R-Truth comes up to reminisce about when he was in Carlito's position.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ba9a0c76-11d9-4ac2-a626-68a8b28c88c4/Screenshot_20240603_175952.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9e349e87-a20d-40f1-a1ef-58c6f7dad1c4/Screenshot_20240603_180610.jpg)

Sami Zayn calls out Chad Gable but the Academy students come out instead. They read a letter from Gable to Sami that says this will only end when Sami grants Gable an IC title match.

Sami grants the match. He starts trying to talk to Alpha Academy but Chad Gable comes from behind with a sneak attack.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/78d9092b-f7cc-4fc0-a85f-4a325a5d65d1/Screenshot_20240603_180904.jpg)

Gable starts berating Otis for not jumping in to attack Sami. Tozawa steps in then starts getting Gable's wrath. Maxxine begs Chad Gable to stop and he forces her to get on her knees to beg.

Otis is close to snapping but he doesn't until Chad Gable throws Sami into him and knocks Maxxine and Tozawa off the apron. Otis then attacks Sami Zayn and leaves.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/abe77082-9b20-44a7-a3e3-bbd2f9c39607/Screenshot_20240603_181022.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4d5573cc-776e-4989-b968-308267f22c67/Screenshot_20240603_181733.jpg)

Gable thanks the Alpha Academy for their plan in taking our Sami Zayn. But none of them were planning anything. They’re really hurt and got ignored.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/001d1c2f-02b3-47a5-87ea-e203121c6f28/Screenshot_20240603_181747.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/059acd20-a2bb-4d94-aea1-72a11316a680/Screenshot_20240603_181917.jpg)

Bron Breakker's got a horrible new theme song.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ab03efd0-107f-4a52-a093-2aaa249ea233/Screenshot_20240603_182524.jpg)

*   ## **_BRON BREAKKER DEF. RICOCHET_**
    

This is the first main roster match for Breakker to go past 30 seconds and it delivered. Finish sees Breakker hitting an INCREDIBLE FrankenSteiner and then a high impact spear to break Ricochet in half.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b6db6148-afc5-4ea4-8f07-ba9ea6cad03f/Screenshot_20240603_182905.jpg)

Bron is going to end Ricochet before security and Ilja Dragunov make the save

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a49f5efa-ab9b-4f5b-a702-0bfee66d901f/Screenshot_20240603_182925.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8839ba5c-7598-465f-a4d7-a90130e1a057/Screenshot_20240603_183922.jpg)

*   ## **_KIANA JAMES DEF. NATALYA_**
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/75d01b9d-db6b-4d5b-869f-d28bab5c6522/Screenshot_20240603_184329.jpg)

New Day are talking to Cathy Kelly when Karrion Kross interrupts to say they just aren’t the same anymore because the Power of Positivity is dead.

Kross then guarantees Woods he won’t have to follow Kofi around after tonight

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/91cca3c6-ae07-46de-aee8-3522c0dc4902/Screenshot_20240603_184355.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/af3b2778-96d5-4ca8-966e-96b1a3681409/Screenshot_20240603_184958.jpg)

*   ## **_BRAUN STROWMAN DEF. CARLITO_**
    

Fairly quick match that ends when Judgement Day tries to interfere and fails. Post match, Braun is beating the numbers game and goes to end Dom.

Liv Morgan comes out and acts as a human shield. Strowman walks away and the Judgement Day FINALLY take care of Braun. All thanks to Liv..

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/bf613137-2316-4fb5-9da8-60a9eff9fe5d/Screenshot_20240603_185216.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/aa1445e1-5df8-42d7-9bb6-03058e840956/Screenshot_20240603_190057.jpg)

Jade Cargill and Bianca Belair are out to answer Shayna Baszler and Zoey Starks invitation to RAW

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/508a094e-2971-420b-ad06-ea9b2213bb97/Screenshot_20240603_190153.jpg)

Zoey and Shayna come out. They call Bianca and Jade cowards. Bianca and Jade challenge them right now.

Adam Pearce makes it official.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/59d83bbb-032c-46df-8dc7-3d8ea29661ba/Screenshot_20240603_190455.jpg)

*   ## **_WWE WOMEN'S TAG TEAM CHAMPIONSHIPS: JADE CARGILL AND BIANCA BELAIR DEF. SHAYNA BASZLER AND ZOEY STARKS_** BY DQ
    

Alba Fyre and Isla Dawn attack Jade and Bianca. Zoey and Shayna join in and leave them lying to end the segment

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/17c8104b-df08-4940-9cb4-c2e60922e1ed/Screenshot_20240603_191346.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3d300ee1-327b-415e-91bd-85864b2720ad/Screenshot_20240603_192010.jpg)

Jey Uso declares for the Money in the Bank Ladder Match… You can do that??

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4ada2347-a164-4b57-ac01-074b321f8875/Screenshot_20240603_192459.jpg)

Lyra Valkyria is inspired by Jey Uso to do the same thing but she's taken out by Iyo Sky. Setting up a match for next week.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ed671479-95f8-405e-936f-f7d389a5b222/Screenshot_20240603_193433.jpg)

*   ## **_AUTHORS OF PAIN DEF. NEW DAY_**
    

AoP keeps Kofi off the turnbuckle when Xavier is looking for a tag. This costs them the match. Xavier looks up to Kofi as if to ask why wasn’t he in the corner.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/11230585-ff73-4bde-88ae-e769fd60eebc/Screenshot_20240603_193501.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/03246d1e-72b6-4493-82b1-4cba55df8cef/Screenshot_20240603_193531.jpg)

Alba Fyre and Isla Dawn say they took matters into their own hands because Clash of the Castle is coming up and they aten’t on the card.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/626f7607-9c50-4951-a556-175c22256fb9/Screenshot_20240603_194505.jpg)

*   ## **_DAMIEN PRIEST DEF. REY MYSTERIO_**
    

Judgement Day get involved and distract Rey enough for him to get chokeslammed to his end.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b3ca4048-0eb5-4dab-af2e-d20af764012d/Screenshot_20240603_200016.jpg)

Drew McIntyre attacks Damien after the match. He’s got the advantage before he gets distracted by Michael Cole and put through a table